Package sailpoint.object

Class NativeChangeDetection

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.object.LinkSnapshot
      • sailpoint.object.NativeChangeDetection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, LinkInterface
    public class NativeChangeDetection
extends LinkSnapshot
    A class used to represent detected native changes found from aggregation to aggregation. These are stored on the identity then processed by the refresh task.
    Since:
    6.0
    See Also:
    Perform native change detection when included in a LifeCycle event. *, Serialized Form
